recipe.label: Lentils and Mozzarella Caprese From 'Feast'
ingredientLines: 1/4 cup (60 ml) plus 2 tablespoons extra-virgin olive oil
1 cup (185 g) green or brown lentils, rinsed
2 tablespoons red wine vinegar or apple cider vinegar
Handful assorted fresh herbs such as dill, chives, basil, or mint, finely chopped
1 cup (510 g) fresh bocconcini mozzarella, torn, or mozzarella, sliced

recipe.label: Japanese Curry from Scratch
ingredientLines: 500 grams onion sliced thin (2 large onions)
2 1/2 tablespoons curry powder Japanese brand such as S&B
300 grams carrots cut into chunks (~ 2 carrots)
1 small apple peeled cored and grated
350 grams potatoes cut into large chunks (~2 medium potatoes)
